{%- comment -%}
  Section 8: Social Proof / Testimonials
  Mix of: pain type diversity, age diversity, specific results.
  Judge.me widget placeholder + manual testimonial cards as fallback.
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="testimonials">
  <div class="testimonials__inner page-width">
    <span class="section-eyebrow">Real People. Real Pain. Real Results.</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading">"I've Tried Everything." So Did They.</h2>
    <p class="section-subheading">These are people who had the drawer full of failed products, the 2 AM Google searches, the crushing disappointment. Here's what changed.</p>

    {%- comment -%} Judge.me widget placeholder {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="testimonials__judgeme" id="judgeme-widget">
      <!-- Judge.me Product Reviews Widget renders here -->
      <!-- Install Judge.me app and add: {{ product.metafields.judgeme.widget }} -->
    </div>

    {%- comment -%} Manual testimonial cards (shown until Judge.me is installed) {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="testimonials__grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__quote">
          "I have a drawer full of things I bought at 2 AM that were supposed to help. Eight products, maybe $500 gone. I almost didn't order this one. But two weeks in, I walked my dog for the first time in four months. I stood there at the end of the street and cried."
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">
          <span class="testimonial-card__name">Margaret T.</span>
          <span class="testimonial-card__detail">Age 63 · Chronic Back Pain · 6 years</span>
          <span class="testimonial-card__verified">✓ Verified Buyer</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__quote">
          "My wife noticed before I did. She said I wasn't groaning when I got out of bed anymore. I didn't even realize I'd been doing that for years. I used to negotiate with my body every morning about what I could and couldn't do. Three weeks in, I just... got up."
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">
          <span class="testimonial-card__name">Robert K.</span>
          <span class="testimonial-card__detail">Age 58 · Sciatica · 4 years</span>
          <span class="testimonial-card__verified">✓ Verified Buyer</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__quote">
          "I was spending $800 a month between cortisone shots and PT. Each shot lasted shorter than the last — first eight weeks, then three weeks, then ten days. I cancelled my next injection for the first time in two years. This belt cost less than one of those shots."
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">
          <span class="testimonial-card__name">Denise W.</span>
          <span class="testimonial-card__detail">Age 61 · Arthritis · 5 years</span>
          <span class="testimonial-card__verified">✓ Verified Buyer</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__quote">
          "I'd cancelled so many plans that people stopped inviting me. My world shrank to my bedroom and my couch. Last Saturday, I was at my grandson's birthday. Standing. In the photos. I'm not pain-free. But I'm not watching from the sidelines anymore."
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">
          <span class="testimonial-card__name">Diane P.</span>
          <span class="testimonial-card__detail">Age 67 · Lower Back & Hip · 8 years</span>
          <span class="testimonial-card__verified">✓ Verified Buyer</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__quote">
          "Retired carpenter. 40 years on my knees. I felt like I was 90 and I'm only 71. PT twice a week, cortisone every 3 months, and I still couldn't stand in my workshop for more than ten minutes. After a month with this belt, I built my granddaughter a bookshelf. My PT asked what changed."
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">
          <span class="testimonial-card__name">Gerald S.</span>
          <span class="testimonial-card__detail">Age 71 · Knee Pain · 9 years</span>
          <span class="testimonial-card__verified">✓ Verified Buyer</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__quote">
          "I hated the pills. The fog. Feeling like a junkie just because my back was broken. My doctor said 'manage your expectations.' I just wanted to cook dinner for my family again. This belt doesn't make me foggy. It doesn't make me feel like an addict. It just... works. I made Sunday dinner last week. First time in two years."
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">
          <span class="testimonial-card__name">Patricia M.</span>
          <span class="testimonial-card__detail">Age 55 · Lower Back & Nerve Pain · 3 years</span>
          <span class="testimonial-card__verified">✓ Verified Buyer</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

